CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 21, 1966, pg. 2A reads: "Delivering Benediction - Rev. C. Leroy Hacker, center, is shown delivering benediction at the Courier-WAMO Negro Market Seminar. Left to right, D. Parke Gibson, Leonard Walk, president, WAMO; Rev. Hacker; Mrs. Eleanor A. Lofton, acting published Pittsburgh Courier and Bernard Howard, president, Bernard Howard & Company. (Harris photo)"
TitMainTitle: D. Parke Gibson, Leonard Walk, Rev. C. Leroy Hacker, Eleanor A. Lofton, and Bernard Howard, standing at head banquet table in Penn Sheraton Hotel, for 1966 Courier-WAMO Negro Market Seminar
